code: public boolean matches(Class<?> type) {     if (parents != null && parents.size() > 0) {         for (Class<?> parent : parents) {             if (parent.isAssignableFrom(type)) {                 return true.             }         }     }     return false. }

@Override public String toString() {     StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder().     for (Class<?> parent : parents) {         sb.append(parent.getSimpleName()).append(", ").     }     sb.setLength(sb.length() > 0 ? sb.length() - 2 : 0).     return "is assignable to any of " + sb. }
